# Trivy Ignore File
# These CVEs affect OS packages in python:3.13-slim (Debian) with no upstream fix.
# Reviewed: 2026-03-30. Re-review by: 2026-06-30.

# ncurses buffer overflow — not used by application code (terminal library)
CVE-2025-69720

# systemd arbitrary code execution — not the init system inside containers
CVE-2026-29111

# nghttp2 DoS — base image residual; curl removed from fuel-ingestor, not installed elsewhere
CVE-2026-27135

# glibc iconv() DoS — fix deferred by Debian; app does not use iconv with untrusted character sets
CVE-2026-4046
